data.description: Experience the essence of mountain living in this expansive 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom cabin-style home, majestically perched in the beautiful city of Crestline. Just a mere 4 minutes away from the relaxing waters of Lake Gregory, this residence offers a unique blend of serenity and adventure.    Spanning 1,368 sqft of tastefully remodeled living space, this two-story gem sits on a generous 9,470 sqft lot. From the moment you step inside, you're captivated by its detailed finishes, including crown molding, stylish baseboards, and window trims. The main floor (downstairs) boasts two comfortable bedrooms and a luxurious bathroom featuring a spacious glass shower with exquisite pebble flooring, and ample downstairs storage space. As you head to the upper level, two more large bedrooms await, complemented by another elegantly remodeled bathroom adorned with light granite countertops.    Step into a beautifully designed interior that seamlessly blends function and style. The kitchen, with its pristine light granite countertops, modern tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and timeless white cabinetry, effortlessly meets all your culinary needs. Adjacent to this is the inviting living area, where a dual-purpose wood-burning and gas fireplace serves as a focal point, setting the mood for those cozy Crestline evenings.    Outdoors, indulge in the panoramic views of scenic mountains and glimpses of the lake through the trees from one of the two expansive decks. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or entertaining guests, these spaces promise relaxation and memorable moments.    While the home has been lovingly updated inside, please note that due to the mountainous weather conditions, the exterior requires some minor attention to restore its original charm. (the home recently had the water main line to the house fully repaired and upgraded.)     Crestline is not just a location; it's a lifestyle. The city continuously hosts engaging community events, and Lake Gregory ensures there's never a dull moment with its year-round water activities.    Seize the opportunity to be a part of this vibrant community and call this mountain paradise your own. Schedule your viewing today!
